The base is on land, Yan, in Mongolia. Im glad that youre on top of it, 
couldnt have done it with out you buddy.

       The missles hit the shields and sent a wave of energy across the force 
feild. Quickly, the EMP Canon targeted the Jets and sent a shot after each of 
them. The missle launchers targeted the bots outside the base and sent spark 
seeking missles after them.
